---
description: API route handlers — validation and Prisma usage
globs: src/app/api/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# API routes (`src/app/api`)

- Export named functions: `GET`, `POST`, `PATCH`, `DELETE` as needed.
- Use `NextRequest` when reading search params or headers.
- Parse JSON with `await request.json()`; validate with Zod for non-trivial payloads.
- Use shared `db` from `@/lib/db` — do not instantiate new Prisma clients per request.
- Return errors as JSON: `Response.json({ error: "..." }, { status: 4xx|5xx })`.
- Keep side effects (queue dispatch, webhooks) idempotent or guarded where duplicates are possible.
